formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.RERA Bank Account details are taken as per  provided by the promoters. The Promoter is maintaining Single Account as RERA Account hence the 100% amount is deposited in that account only.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement We conducted our examination of the Statement in accordance with the Guidance Note on Reports or Certificates for Special Purposes issued by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project  solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA. While computing withdrawls from the bank account, we have considered total receipts during the period and balance lying in RERA Bank Account as base for computing withdrawable amount on account of construction. Moreover the promotoers have parked 100% the amount received from the customers in the RERA account as against the requirement of 70%.While computing deposits and withdrawls from the bank, the promoter has a system of sweep MOD, hence we have taken opening balance as on 01/07/2019 and added deposits and reduced withdrawls, this also contains sweep debit and sweep credit transactions, the closing balance is arrived at after adding deposits and withdrawls from the opening balance. No lien is created on the MOD Balance with SBI Account.Promoter has paid Advance towards Labour and material amounting to Rs 15419023/-. The same has been added to cost incurrred and Paid.Unit consideration amount is inclusive of GST, hence for arriving at amount withdrawn from separate RERA A/c, we have reduced amount of GST i.e 9067595/-from the amount withdrawn. As the incurred and paid cost does not inlcude GST Portion in it. Promoter has only one seperate RERA A/c and all the booking deposit is being parked there only and all withdrawls are made from that account only.Promoter has not taken any project loan but has taken unsecured loan and interest paid on the same is part of incurred and paid cost. The Project has received Building Use Permission as on 27/11/2019 hence the requirement of maintaining seperate RERA Account is no longer required.We have submitted the same data as taken in the earlier CA Certificate as Form 1 and form 2 is taken the same way.
